<HEAD>Fishermen Shot by Egyptian Helicopter, 15 Wounded In Clashes</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: Leads with 4 grafs to UPDATE with army confirmaton on jailed
reservist; picks up 5th pvs: Two wounded...; SUBS 12th graf pvs,
`Arab reporters...' with one graf to UPDATE with army comment;
picks up 13th pvs: The worst...; SUBS last two grafs to conform; no
