   _Moderates, 17.9 percent, 64
   _Center Party, 11.9 percent, 43
   _Liberals, 12 percent, 43
   _Communists, 5.7 percent, 21
   _Greens, 5.5 percent, 20
   _Christian Democrats, 3.1 percent, 0
